**Option 1 is even more clearly the right choice** because:
✅ **Balanced modernization** - not bleeding edge, not obsolete  
✅ **Infrastructure ready for EBS migration** - containerized APIs, APIM  
✅ **Security compliance** - Okta, TLS 1.2, vulnerability fixes  
✅ **Reasonable effort** - 420 hours for comprehensive modernization  
✅ **Strategic alignment** - prepares for gradual EBS migration  

The additional requirements make this a proper infrastructure modernization project that sets C2G up for success in the long-term EBS migration strategy.
